        0.2.2 (2018-05-08)
        ==================
        
        Fixes:
        
        * Update travis for Python 3.x (#19).
        * Fix parsing of WPS capabilities with ``%`` (#18).
        
        New Features:
        
        * using ``mode`` for async execution in OWSLib (#22).
        
        0.2.1 (2018-03-14)
        ==================
        
        Fixes:
        
        * Fixed Sphinx and updated docs: #15.
        
        New Features:
        
        * Fix #14: added ``--cert`` option to use x509 certificates.
        
